></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-teal-primary/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-10 w-10 text-teal-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-teal-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Log In Securely</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Patients sign in with the same credentials they use for your Virtual Practice web portal. This ensures secure access and a unified experience across web and mobile.</p><div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 -right-4 text-teal-primary/30"><svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-success/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart h-10 w-10 text-green-success" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-green-success text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Access Care Anytime</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Once logged in, patients can book appointments, view records, pay bills, and sync health data from Apple Health, Google Health Connect, or supported devices.</p><div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-10 -right-4 text-green-success/30"><svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></div></div><div class="text-center relative"><div class="relative mb-6"><div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-accent/10 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-bell h-10 w-10 text-purple-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10.268 21a2 2 0 0 0 3.464 0"></path><path d="M3.262 15.326A1 1 0 0 0 4 17h16a1 1 0 0 0 .74-1.673C19.41 13.956 18 12.499 18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 4.499-1.411 5.956-2.738 7.326"></path></svg></div><div class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</div></div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-3">Stay Connected</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Patients receive push notifications for appointments, lab results, and care plan updates — keeping them engaged with your practice between visits.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Success Stories</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->Virtual Practice platform is delivering next-generation medical care. As a multidisciplinary team, we find it powerful and intuitive for organizing patient cases, with clear medical records that support precise documentation and effective care.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Georgios Leon - Metabolic Specialist</p><p class="text-gray-600">Precision Medicine Startup, Greece</p></div></div></div><div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full"><p class="text-gray-700 italic mb-4">&quot;<!-- -->I have been using the continuous care platform for several months and it has made a big impact in my practice, allowing me to monitor my patients more efficiently.<!-- -->&quot;</p><div><p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Dr. Marie Christina Felix Douyon</p><p class="text-gray-600">Pulmonologist, Haiti</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What is the Patient Mobile App in the Virtual Practice?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The Patient Mobile App is the native iOS and Android application that comes with your Virtual Practice. It lets patients securely log in, book appointments, view health records, pay bills, and communicate with providers — all from their smartphones."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the Patient Mobile App free for clinics to use?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Every Virtual Practice includes access to the free ContinuousCare patient app, which patients can download from the iOS App Store or Google Play. Clinics don't need to pay extra for their patients to use it."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I have the app under my own brand name?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Startups and clinics that want their own branded app can choose the white-label option. This paid add-on publishes the app under your organization's App Store and Play Store accounts, with your name, logo, and branding."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What can patients do with the app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patients can:\n\nBook video or in-person appointments\n\nView prescriptions, test results, and medical history\n\nReceive smart notifications and reminders\n\nPay bills online\n\nManage family member accounts\n\nSync health data automatically from supported devices"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does the app integrate with Apple Health and Google Health Connect?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Patients can grant permission to sync data from Apple Health (iOS) or Google Health Connect (Android) directly into their Virtual Practice health record. White-label apps also support additional Bluetooth health device integrations."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the Patient Mobile App secure?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The app follows the same security and compliance standards as the Virtual Practice web portal. Data is encrypted in transit and at rest, and only patients and their authorized providers can view health information."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers send information to patients through the app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Providers can share prescriptions, lab results, consultation notes, and care plan updates directly in the app. Patients receive instant notifications when new information is available."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do patients still have access to the web portal if they use the app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The web portal and the mobile app are fully synchro